title: Pukenza collection released free for Doodlers
body:
Doodle ID for kudos:  #276

Discourse:  https://forum.doodles.app/t/pukenza-airdrop-for-doods/367

Rationale: This art is awesome and it would be a nice little treat for Doodle holders whilst rewarding an artist that is deeply involved with the Doodles community! WestcoastNFT, the company who handled Doodles’ web3 dev needs, will be assisting in this drop as well.

Timeline: Pukenzas will be available for either claiming or airdrop 4-6 weeks after the proposal is finalized.  This allows time for polishing the algorithm for the generative art + testing and smart contract preparation.

Goals: Offer the Pukenza generative artwork to all Doodle Holders for free. Doodlers will either pay gas to claim or receive polygon airdrop.

Cost:  4.20 ETH total cost 
•	3ETH to L3xc for artwork 
•	1.2 ETH to WestcoastNFT for smart contract development + contract deployment gas fee + website development
•	7.5% royalty on secondary sales going to L3xc

Accountability:
•	Funds will be transferred into gnosis multisig with tulip/burnt/poopie as cosigners in a 4/5 policy
•	Funds will be paid out on delivery of completed user stories found in final proposal

Options: 
Yes – Mainnet: I will pay my own gas to mint Pukenza on Ethereum mainnet in exchange for the chance of higher secondary value
Yes – Polygon: I want all 10,000 Pukenzas to be minted on Polygon and distributed to all Doodler’s wallets for free
No: I don’t want the free Pukenza
author: 0xD857EC5EF3775295C5Cc4d1fe259D5EBa98bDA23
